1
00:00:37,300 --> 00:00:40,580
=Reincarnated Love=

2
00:00:40,780 --> 00:00:43,700
=Episode 8=

3
00:00:43,700 --> 00:00:45,940
(Huo Mansion)

4
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:14,840
Milady.

5
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:16,080
- Milady.
- Tao.

6
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:17,710
None of the 37 kitchen helpers

7
00:01:18,060 --> 00:01:18,920
from Chunman Tavern

8
00:01:18,920 --> 00:01:19,870
knows Ruyan.

9
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:22,220
She lied

10
00:01:22,231 --> 00:01:23,510
about her childhood acquaintance.

11
00:01:24,310 --> 00:01:25,560
This is indeed suspicious.

12
00:01:26,590 --> 00:01:27,560
Has Mr. Huo returned?

13
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:28,600
Just now...

14
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:32,430
I'll take my leave.

15
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:35,680
You came home so late.

16
00:01:35,950 --> 00:01:37,230
I've prepared calming tea,

17
00:01:37,241 --> 00:01:38,203
waiting for your return.

18
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:41,480
Waiting for me?

19
00:01:42,430 --> 00:01:43,640
How thoughtful of you.

20
00:01:46,230 --> 00:01:47,350
I can't wait

21
00:01:47,350 --> 00:01:48,920
for others anyway.

22
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,446
You said you've been waiting for me.

23
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:00,920
You look weighed down by worries.

24
00:02:04,870 --> 00:02:05,710
Go on then.

25
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,560
What happened?

26
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,240
Just a while ago,

27
00:02:12,470 --> 00:02:14,120
Ruyan's twin sister, Ruyi,

28
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,360
came here asking for Ruyan.

29
00:02:16,030 --> 00:02:16,870
Ruyan...

30
00:02:17,750 --> 00:02:18,750
Ruyan might have

31
00:02:18,910 --> 00:02:19,750
met with misfortune.

32
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,400
Ruyan?

33
00:02:26,030 --> 00:02:27,430
This is Ruyan's farewell letter.

34
00:02:31,980 --> 00:02:33,880
(Ruyi, by the time you read this,
I'd be dead.)

35
00:02:33,891 --> 00:02:35,040
(Please don't blame my lady.)

36
00:02:48,310 --> 00:02:49,150
Don't worry.

37
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:51,240
Leave this to me.

38
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,280
As your husband,

39
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,520
it's my duty to see it through.

40
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:57,520
Thank you.

41
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:59,120
From now on,

42
00:03:01,150 --> 00:03:03,430
whatever happens,

43
00:03:03,430 --> 00:03:04,910
let me know right away.

44
00:03:05,750 --> 00:03:07,280
I don't want someone else to help you.

45
00:03:19,630 --> 00:03:20,560
Search thoroughly.

46
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:27,030
Shitou, over here.

47
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,200
Ruyan...

48
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:56,990
Ruyan...

49
00:03:59,710 --> 00:04:00,750
I'm here.

50
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:30,630
Ruyi,

51
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:33,520
don't worry.

52
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:36,240
About Ruyan's death,

53
00:04:38,310 --> 00:04:40,160
I'll make sure you get an answer.

54
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,240
Thank you, milady.

55
00:04:53,190 --> 00:04:54,070
Ruyan...

56
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:15,113
The informant I placed
in Jiang Mansion told me

57
00:05:15,310 --> 00:05:17,390
they saw Ruyan go there
late at night many times,

58
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:18,400
looking suspicious.

59
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:22,830
I didn't find the man

60
00:05:23,190 --> 00:05:23,860
Ruyan spoke of

61
00:05:23,871 --> 00:05:25,413
among Chunman Tavern's kitchen helpers.

62
00:05:26,630 --> 00:05:28,096
I don't think the child Ruyan carried

63
00:05:28,830 --> 00:05:30,120
is as simple as we thought.

64
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,920
I'll keep investigating.

65
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:35,750
Especially those she last met.

66
00:05:42,340 --> 00:05:45,420
(Huo Mansion)

67
00:05:48,870 --> 00:05:49,870
Still not awake?

68
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:51,920
Yuan.

69
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,390
I had the kitchen make

70
00:05:53,390 --> 00:05:54,750
some Jade Shrimp Dumplings.

71
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:56,600
See if they suit your taste.

72
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,600
(My wife's nickname)

73
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,480
(is not for outsiders to address.)

74
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:03,640
Yuan?

75
00:06:07,190 --> 00:06:08,030
Try them.

76
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:14,880
Thank you, Huaijin.

77
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:28,920
Hey, don't eat too much.

78
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:29,760
Don't...

79
00:06:34,950 --> 00:06:36,480
I know you care for me,

80
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:38,270
knowing I'm swamped with affairs,

81
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:39,830
so you had this made for me.

82
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:41,360
I'll finish every bite.

83
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:53,000
Where's Ruoli?

84
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,680
Last night,

85
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:57,990
Yuan and I...

86
00:07:01,390 --> 00:07:02,600
She's exhausted now.

87
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,720
Still in asleep.

88
00:07:04,870 --> 00:07:07,000
In that case, I'll take my leave.

89
00:07:07,190 --> 00:07:08,030
Hey, Huaijin.

90
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,510
You're awake,

91
00:07:34,510 --> 00:07:35,350
Yuan.

92
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,870
Jade Shrimp Dumplings.

93
00:07:39,390 --> 00:07:40,230
Are they tasty?

94
00:07:41,390 --> 00:07:42,230
Delicious.

95
00:07:45,870 --> 00:07:47,070
They just need more vinegar.

96
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:06,000
That shameless Jiang Ruoli

97
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:08,510
has Huo Linchuan shielding her now.

98
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,226
She suppresses you at every turn.

99
00:08:10,870 --> 00:08:12,360
Do you have a way to turn this around?

100
00:08:13,510 --> 00:08:14,350
Father,

101
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:15,830
Jiang Ruoli

102
00:08:15,830 --> 00:08:17,200
is cunning to the core.

103
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:20,160
It's not that she's cunning.

104
00:08:20,310 --> 00:08:21,510
It's you who's far too naive.

105
00:08:23,070 --> 00:08:25,430
Jiang Ruoli relies on Huo Linchuan.

106
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,290
Huo is a tough one

107
00:08:27,510 --> 00:08:29,630
to deal with.

108
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:33,800
Oh, right.

109
00:08:34,150 --> 00:08:37,750
Isn't there a man named Lu Huaijin?

110
00:08:38,030 --> 00:08:39,510
Go and get close to him.

111
00:08:39,510 --> 00:08:40,350
Win his favor.

112
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:42,840
Once we get close to the Huo clan,

113
00:08:43,510 --> 00:08:44,350
we'll have

114
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:47,080
plenty of chances ahead.

115
00:08:47,390 --> 00:08:48,240
Father,

116
00:08:48,270 --> 00:08:50,200
Lu Huaijin is merely an adopted son.

117
00:08:50,390 --> 00:08:51,840
You're asking me to charm him?

118
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:53,480
I'm a noble lady.

119
00:08:53,630 --> 00:08:54,470
I refuse to do it.

120
00:08:54,630 --> 00:08:55,750
What's wrong with that?

121
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,790
Huo Linchuan may not have secured

122
00:08:57,910 --> 00:08:59,720
the heir position.

123
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:01,360
If you can marry Lu,

124
00:09:01,630 --> 00:09:03,150
we can help him

125
00:09:03,510 --> 00:09:04,870
take the heir position,

126
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:06,510
and you'll be the heir's wife.

127
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,040
By that time,

128
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:10,080
Jiang Ruoli will be under our control.

129
00:09:11,670 --> 00:09:12,510
Go right now.

130
00:09:13,030 --> 00:09:15,360
Find a way to meet Lu Huaijin.

131
00:09:16,020 --> 00:09:17,069
If I go to the Huo Mansion,

132
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:18,360
how will Jiang Ruoli see me?

133
00:09:19,470 --> 00:09:20,340
Father,

134
00:09:20,390 --> 00:09:22,080
what about my dignity?

135
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,080
Dignity?

136
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:25,080
What dignity do we have left?

137
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:27,030
If you marry an heir,

138
00:09:27,670 --> 00:09:30,120
today's humiliation will mean nothing.

139
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:32,090
- But...
- Enough!

140
00:09:33,030 --> 00:09:34,790
Go as I said.

141
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:38,670
I understand.

142
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:13,120
♪The dream shattered♪

143
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:15,160
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

144
00:10:15,160 --> 00:10:16,800
♪Like a restless soul♪

145
00:10:17,680 --> 00:10:19,240
♪How vague♪

146
00:10:19,640 --> 00:10:21,160
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

147
00:10:21,160 --> 00:10:23,400
♪A blade of frost in dreams♪

148
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:26,800
♪Love and hate entwined♪

149
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:30,120
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

150
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:35,520
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

151
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:37,640
♪When fate falls apart♪

152
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:41,600
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

153
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:43,880
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

154
00:10:44,280 --> 00:10:48,000
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

155
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:51,560
♪Life after life♪

156
00:10:52,040 --> 00:10:54,720
♪Fated to meet, but never meant to be♪

157
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:59,440
♪Still, I refuse to bow or yield♪

158
00:10:59,520 --> 00:11:02,560
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

159
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:04,120
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

160
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:07,240
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

161
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:08,760
♪Now shatter apart♪

162
00:11:08,880 --> 00:11:12,640
♪By fate and karmic ties confined♪

163
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:16,160
♪Is this fate or calamity♪

164
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:19,280
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

165
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:24,000
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

166
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:27,160
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

167
00:11:27,280 --> 00:11:31,720
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

168
00:11:31,920 --> 00:11:37,640
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

169
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:40,800
♪This fleeting life feels but a dream♪

170
00:11:41,040 --> 00:11:43,760
♪Sober or indulge♪

171
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:50,200
♪I only wish to be with you,
with all my heart♪
